Invocation Name: breast check
des:
1 in 8 women will be diagnosed with breast cancer. And almost half of all breast cancers are found by women checking their own breasts. This breast health skill from the breast cancer charity I Touch Myself Project gives women access to the latest instructions and information on how to get to know what’s normal and how to check their breasts for changes.

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
